text: The 2012 King's Cup is an international football tournament that was held in Thailand from 15 to 21 January 2012. The 4 national teams involved in the tournament were required to register a squad of 25 players. Only players in these squads were eligible to take part in the tournament. ==Squads== ===Denmark League XI=== Head coach: Morten Olsen === Norway === Head coach: Egil Olsen === South Korea U-23 === Head coach: Hong Myung-Bo ===Thailand=== Head coach: Winfried Schäfer ==References== ==External links== * King's Cup * Football in Thailand Category:2012 in Thai football cups Category:King's Cup
